<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Speakeasy!</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      background: #e3f2fd;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #1e88e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 5px solid #1565c0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1, h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #1e88e5;
    }

    ol {
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .avatar {
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      width: 150px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    button {
      background-color: #1e88e5;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      color: white;
      font-size: 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #1565c0;
    }

    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Speakeasy! üåç</h1>
    <p>Learn languages the fun way with interactive games!</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>How to Get Started:</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Pick a language you want to practice.</li>
      <li>Scroll through exciting games like Word Match, Flashcards, or Finish the Sentence.</li>
      <li>Read the description of the game to see what it's about.</li>
      <li>Hit the <strong>‚ÄúStart Game‚Äù</strong> button to dive in.</li>
      <li>Follow the instructions, earn points, and hit a new high score!</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="button-container">
      <button onclick="location.href='/games'">Start Exploring Games</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
